QuestData.Title: Can't Turn Our Backs
QuestData.Description:
That's Sylvanas and her Mawsworn dealt with... for now.
But we need to hurry and make sure that the Queen and her sigil are safe!
The Winter Queen was just outside the Heart of the Forest, protecting the stolen wildseeds from the Maw.
QuestData.RewardText:
Ardenweald depends on the cycle. Without these spirits, what purpose would there be?
I could not let the Jailer's forces destroy what we have fought so hard to protect.
